      <div class="verisol_graphic -slide-1-1"></div>
        <h3>Easy-to-use dashboards</h3>
  <p>
    See important trends by team, department or across the entire fleet. Easily review your progress
    towards achieving and maintaining KPIs.
  </p>

    </div>
    <div class="verisol_sub-section verisol_slide" data-slide-label="Detailed maps">
      <div class="verisol_graphic -slide-1-2"></div>
        <h3>Detailed maps</h3>
  <p>
    High-resolution maps with smart clustering and detail on demand provide a simple, yet powerful,
    tool to view the real-time activity and current status of all your vehicles, workers and mobile
    equipment, no matter where they are.
  </p>

    </div>
    <div class="verisol_sub-section verisol_slide" data-slide-label="Productivity / utilization">
      <div class="verisol_graphic -slide-1-3"></div>
        <h3>Improved productivity through better utilization</h3>
  <p>
    The first step to improving productivity is
    being able to take stock of what you have and how it’s being used. Better fleet visibility allows
    you improve asset utilization, allowing you to get more done with fewer resources.
  </p>

    </div>
    <div class="verisol_sub-section verisol_slide" data-slide-label="Access from anywhere">
      <div class="verisol_graphic -slide-1-4"></div>
        <h3>Access from anywhere</h3>
  <p>
    The industry’s fastest web-based maps are accessible from any device with an internet connection.
    Supervisors or drivers out in the field can see the same view a manager has back in the office.
  </p>

    </div>
